programme.title: Julia
programme.desc: Thriller about a woman who, after suffering a brutal rape, falls prey to a doctor's unorthodox form of therapy that has rape victims taking back power from their attackers, which leads to her embarking on a series of attacks as a way to empower herself by humiliating them. Comedy, starring Eddie Murphy in multiple roles alongside Thandie Newton, Cuba Gooding Jr and Terry Crews(n).

Comedy, starring Jim Carrey, Jennifer Aniston and Morgan Freeman(n).

Comedy, starring Corey Haim, Corey Feldman, Carol Kane and Heather Graham(n).(n)
